    "description": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>YES CONSTRUCTION PTE LTD</strong>&nbsp;was incorporated in 30 March 2007.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">The company policy is Quality and Teamwork, combining together to provide a dedicated service and commitment to serve our customers with the most cost effective solution without compromising the quality and project duration.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">The organization is moving on its way to become a reputable builder, formulating a team of administrative and technical staffs, capable in its respective field of expertise. Together with the co-operation and assistance from our regular suppliers, sub-contractors, and other specialists in their respective trades, we provide the assurance to potential clients, consultants and developers that we are continuously striving towards innovative methods and perfection.</span></span></p>\r\n",
